  "drug_susc_impact": "Loss of RshA leads to increased susceptibility to certain drugs, while overexpression can confer resistance. Specifically, it's linked to altered susceptibility to:",
  "infection_impact": "RshA influences the ability of *M. tuberculosis* to survive and replicate within macrophages, impacting its virulence and persistence.",
